# 🧪 MCS Workshop Agent – Lab Setup Instructions

Follow these step-by-step instructions to get started with your lab environment.

---

## ✅ Step 1: Open the Training Agent Portal
Go to 👉 [https://aka.ms/MCSWorkshopAgent](https://aka.ms/MCSWorkshopAgent)  
Click on **"Chat with training agent"**

---

## 🔑 Step 2: Enter Your Access Code
When prompted, enter the code:  
`ABC-0525-Z0K1`  
Click **Submit**

---

## 👤 Step 3: Get Your User Account
- Click on **"Get user account"**
- Accept the **consent**
- Fill in your details (name, email, etc.)
- Click **Submit**

---

## 🧾 Step 4: Receive Your Credentials
Copy your **training username** and **temporary password** shown after submitting.

---

## 🌐 Step 5: Set Up a New Browser Profile
Create a **new browser profile** (Chrome/Edge/Firefox) to avoid account conflicts.

---

## 🔁 Step 6: Open the Agent Portal Again
In your new browser profile, go to:  
👉 [https://aka.ms/MCSWorkshopAgent](https://aka.ms/MCSWorkshopAgent)

---

## 💬 Step 7: Open Microsoft Copilot Studio
Open a **new tab** and visit:  
👉 [https://copilotstudio.microsoft.com](https://copilotstudio.microsoft.com)

---

## 🔐 Step 8: Login and Reset Password
- Sign in using your training credentials
- Reset your password as prompted

---

## 📚 Step 9: Access the Lab Guides
Browse to:  
👉 [https://aka.ms/mcsworkshoplabs](https://aka.ms/mcsworkshoplabs)

---

## 🚀 Step 10: You're Ready!
Follow the lab guides and start your workshop journey!

---

✅ **All Set! Good luck and enjoy learning!**
